line_1: There lie, in marks indelible engrav'd,
line_2: The means whereby my country must be sav'd;

line_1: His royal master's name thereon engrav'd,
line_2: Without more process, the whole race enslav'd,

line_1: Has choicest prints by famous hands engraved;
line_2: That Bible, bought by sixpence weekly saved,
Their Force destroy'd, their Privileges sav'd,
